out%2C%20the%20front-desk%20manager%20assumed%20my%20husband%20would%20be%20paying%2C%20not%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20religious%20and%20traditional%20settings%2C%20I%20also%20encountered%20different%20standards%20for%20men's%20and%20women's%20dress%20codes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20when%20we%20visited%20the%20Sheikh%20Zayed%20Grand%20Mosque%20%E2%80%94%20about%20an%20hour's%20drive%20outside%20Dubai%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20%E2%80%94%20my%20husband%20and%20sons%20were%20allowed%20entry%20wearing%20shorts%20and%20short-sleeve%20shirts.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20as%20a%20woman%2C%20I%20had%20to%20cover%20my%20hair%2C%20ankles%2C%20and%20wrists%20to%20visit%20the%20mosque.%20I%20ended%20up%20purchasing%20a%20head%20wrap%20and%20wearing%20a%20conservative%20outfit.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20most%20touristy%20areas%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20could%20wear%20what%20I%20wanted%2C%20but%20in%20more%20local%20places%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20to%20dress%20more%20modestly%20and%20fully%20cover%20my%20arms%20and%20legs%20out%20of%20respect%20for%20local%20customs%20and%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22578c7832-0887-4eea-b54c-1e741aec21f3%5C%22%3EWe%20weren't%20prepared%20for%20unexpected%20rain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222511%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20and%20her%20family%20in%20Dubai%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6957e95a832e0ef1ead713ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221884%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDubai%20was%20a%20memorable%20and%20culturally%20rich%20vacation%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Knowles%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20the%20government%20can%20help%20trigger%20rainfall%20through%20cloud%20seeding%2C%20a%20weather-modification%20technique%20that%20addresses%20water%20challenges%20across%20the%20country.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20conditions%20allow%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-cloud-seeding-dubai-photos-how-make-rain-weather-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUnited%20Arab%20Emirates%20National%20Meteorology%3C%2Fa%3E%20flies%20planes%20into%20the%20clouds%20to%20release%20materials%20that%20help%20produce%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20part%20because%20of%20this%2C%20although%20rain%20was%20not%20in%20the%20forecast%2C%20it%20still%20fell%20on%20us%20unexpectedly.%20If%20I%20were%20to%20return%2C%20I%20might%20try%20to%20keep%20a%20rain%20poncho%20and%20umbrella%20in%20my%20bag%20at%20all%20times.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a8e219d-5de1-4e0f-87a4-70887e83ebbe%5C%22%3EI%20hadn't%20thought%20to%20check%20ahead%20of%20time%20to%20see%20if%20we'd%20be%20visiting%20during%20local%20holidays%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20traveled%20to%20Dubai%20during%20Ramadan%2C%20a%20holy%20month%20in%20the%20Islamic%20calendar%20that%20consists%20of%20fasting%2C%20communal%20prayer%2C%20reflection%2C%20and%20community.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20this%20was%20happening%20until%20we%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20many%20places%20were%20still%20open%2C%20some%20had%20adjusted%20hours%20for%20the%20month%20or%20ceased%20activities%20during%20daily%20prayer%20times.%20To%20be%20respectful%2C%20our%20tour%20guide%20also%20advised%20us%20not%20to%20eat%20or%20drink%20anything%20(not%20even%20water)%20in%20public%20from%20sunrise%20to%20sundown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20this%20was%20a%20huge%20deal%2C%20but%20I%20wish%20I'd%20been%20aware%20that%20our%20travel%20time%20coincided%20with%20this%20period%20before%20we%20left.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20said%2C%20even%20knowing%20what%20I%20know%20now%2C%20I'd%20happily%20visit%20Dubai%20again%20in%20the%20future%20%E2%80%94%20and%20next%20time%2C%20I'll%20feel%20more%20prepared.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-know-before-visiting-dubai-with-family-from-american-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv