D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffavorite-florida-state-parks-recommendations-from-local%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emajor%20tourist%20cities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20always%20carry%20an%20over-the-shoulder%20belt%20bag%20to%20keep%20my%20money%2C%20passport%2C%20phone%2C%20and%20cards%20safe%20and%20within%20arm's%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20bags%20are%20also%20practical%20for%20sightseeing.%20For%20instance%2C%20I%20went%20on%20a%20three-hour%20walking%20tour%20of%20St.%20Mark's%20Basilica%20in%20Venice%2C%20and%20wanted%20to%20participate%20without%20worrying%20about%20carrying%20or%20keeping%20track%20of%20my%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20hands-free%20for%20big%20activities%20like%20this%20always%20makes%20the%20experience%20more%20convenient%20and%20enjoyable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20I'm%20done%20bringing%20outfits%20I'll%20only%20wear%20once.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chloe%20smiles%20over%20her%20shoulder%20while%20posing%20on%20a%20bridge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6957d3cc64858d02d217a698%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EChloe%20Caldwell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPlanning%20outfits%20for%20a%20trip%20is%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20parts%20of%20travel%20prep.%20I%20love%20to%20dress%20on%20theme%20and%20get%20a%20snapshot%20of%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20my%20last%20trip%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20packing%20items%20I'll%20only%20wear%20once%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20just%20isn't%20worth%20the%20hassle.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20packed%20a%20long%20red%20gown%20to%20wear%20just%20in%20case%20we%20went%20to%20a%20fancy%20dinner.%20And%2C%20yes%2C%20it%20did%20sit%20folded%20in%20my%20suitcase%20for%20two%20weeks.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20time%2C%20I'll%20bring%20more%20versatile%20items%20that%20I%20can%20mix%20and%20match%20for%