nd%20pursue%20BBQ.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20he's%20diversifying%20his%20income%20streams%20to%20make%20sure%20he's%20prepared%20for%20retirement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Jeremy%20Yoder%2C%20founder%20of%20Mad%20Scientist%20BBQ.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20assumed%20I'd%20become%20a%20doctor%20%E2%80%94%20the%20respectable%20kind%20of%20job%20that%20made%20sense%20to%20my%20family%20and%20community.%20Now%2C%20I%20make%20a%20living%20cooking%20huge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-ultimate-guide-to-beef-cuts-2013-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecuts%20of%20meat%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20camera%20and%20talking%20about%20heat%20transfer%2C%20airflow%2C%20and%20collagen%20breakdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sounds%20like%20a%20wild%20pivot%2C%20but%20for%20me%2C%20each%20step%20%E2%80%94%20leaving%20pre-med%2C%20starting%20and%20then%20quitting%20teaching%2C%20and%20building%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-insider-youtube-channel-wins-diamond-play-button%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20scratch%20%E2%80%94%20came%20from%20the%20same%20place%3A%20wanting%20to%20protect%20my%20family's%20future%20while%20staying%20true%20to%20who%20I%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20believed%20that%20the%20regret%20of%20trying%20and%20failing%20is%20much%20easier%20to%20deal%20with%20than%20the%20regret%20of%20never%20having%20tried%2C%20and%20that%20has%20shaped%20everything%20I've%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a542cb8-12d7-443f-bb90-a1c4cbfccf14%5C%22%3EI%20planned%20to%20build%20my%20career%20around%20science%20and%20medicine%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20Amish%20until%20my%20parents%20left%20the%20community%20when%20I%20was%20in%20elementary%20school.%20Once%20we%20got%20a%20television%2C%20I%20found%20I%20loved%20watching%20the%20Discovery%20and%20Science%20Channels%20and%20learning%20how%20the%20world%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20school%2C%20I%20participated%20in%20academic%20science%20competitions%20and%20studied%20biochemistry%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20pursuing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-paying-healthcare-jobs-high-school-no-bachelors-masters-degree-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecareer%20in%20medicine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20I%20joined%20a%20program%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Louisville%20to%20shadow%20physicians.%20Instead%20of%20showing%20me%20the%20path%20forward%2C%20what%20it%20taught%20was%20that%20I%20didn't%20want%20that%20life.%20Many%20of%20the%20doctors%20I%20worked%20with%20seemed%20miserable%2C%20despite%20having%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalaries-highest-paying-jobs-doctor-surgeon-healthcare-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egood%20salaries%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20nice%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20the%20picture%20I%20had%20of%20being%20a%20doctor%20%E2%80%94%20stability%2C%20meaning%2C%20community%20%E2%80%94%20wasn't%20the%20reality%20I%20was%20seeing.%20So%20I%20moved%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20to%20study%20biblical%20languages%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20understand%20the%20Bible%20better%20and%20think%20more%20deeply%20about%20meaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20support%20myself%2C%20I%20taught%20at%20a%20private%20school%20in%20Woodland%20Hills.%20I%20taught%20almost%20everything%3A%20English%2C%20chemistry%2C%20biology%2C%20AP%20biology%2C%20and%20led%20the%20science%20program.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20making%20an%20impact%2C%20but%20I%20was%20also%20struggling%20to%20pay%20my%20rent%20while%20watching%20kids%20get%20picked%20up%20in%20Rolls-Royces.%20I%20knew%20it%20wasn't%20a%20long-term%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20I%20got%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-holiday-weekend-reminder-that-grilling-is-awesome-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eobsessed%20with%20barbecue%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20watched%20Central%20Texas%20pitmasters%20transform%20tough%20briskets%20into%20something%20tender%20and%20smoky%2C%20and%20I%20realized%20that%20some%20online%20barbecue%20creators%20were%20explaining%20the%20science%20incorrectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20figured%20maybe%20I%20had%20something%20I%20could%20contribute%20given%20my%20interest%20in%20the%20subject%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20I'd%20regret%20it%20if%20I%20didn't%20try.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22573f11db-6a01-4890-b5cf-0458ad9edcab%5C%22%3EMy%20first%20videos%20took%20off%20%E2%80%94%20and%20my%20students%20noticed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20posted%20a%20few%20videos%2C%20and%20they%20performed%20well.%20When%20I%20walked%20into%20school%2C%20one%20of%20my%20students%20saw%20me%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Yoder%2C%20you're%20famous.%26quot%3B%20I%20wasn't%2C%20but%20it%20told%20me%20people%20were%20connecting%20with%20the%20way%20I%20explained%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20noticed%20Los%20Angeles%20didn't%20have%20much%20great%20barbecue.%20I%20thought%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20can%20teach%20all%20day%20and%20still%20cook%20all%20night%2C%20maybe%20I%20can%20make%20this%20work.%26quot%3B%20I%20started%20catering%20events%20on%20the%20side%20%E2%80%94%20rooftop%20pop-ups%20and%20brewery%20gigs%20where%20they%20couldn't%20serve%20food%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20year%20was%20brutal.%20I%20would%20finish%20teaching%2C%20tutor%20until%207%3A30%2C%20walk%20out%20to%20my%20%24500%20truck%2C%20drive%20to%20the%20desert%2C%20cook%20overnight%2C%20clean%20up%2C%20go%20home%2C%20sleep%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%2C%20and%20be%20back%20at%20work%20on%20Monday.%20But%20it%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20viable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffood-industry-entrepreneurs-chefs-owners-navigate-restaurant-strategies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecatering%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20I%20pivoted%20hard%20to%20YouTube.%20Gatherings%20were%20outlawed%2C%20my%20catering%20income%20evaporated%2C%20and%20my%20wife%20was%20five%20months%20pregnant.%20I%20realized%20I%20could%20film%20videos%20without%20needing%20anyone%20else%20around%2C%20so%20we%20started%20posting%20once%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20audience%20seemed%20to%20respond%2C%20and%20the%20subscriber%20numbers%20kept%20growing.%20By%20the%20time%20pandemic%20restrictions%20eased%2C%20YouTube%20had%20outpaced%20catering%20in%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20how%20much%20I%20enjoyed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c7297009-6545-447f-a9fc-2d6d65e8c92d%5C%22%3EI've%20diversified%20revenue%2C%20so%20I'm%20not%20trapped%20on%20camera%20forever%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20assume%20I%20have%20a%20big%20team.%20Really%2C%20my%20wife%20films%2099%25%20of%20my%20videos%20and%20edits%20almost%20all%20of%20them.%20She%20handles%20the%20creative%20vision%3B%20I%20handle%20the%20science%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-cook-and-bake-better-at-home%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecooking%20process%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20typical%20day%20starts%20with%20taking%20our%20daughter%20to%20school%2C%20then%20sitting%20in%20my%20office%20with%20a%20yellow%20legal%20pad.%20I%20sketch%20ideas%2C%20make%20calls%2C%20and%20test%20concepts%2C%20like%20wrapping%20a%20brisket%20in%20clarified%20butter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20cook%20days%2C%20I%20might%20spend%2024%20to%2030%20hours%20on%20a%20single%20brisket%20video.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20I%20take%20my%20daughter%20to%20the%20park.%20I%20have%20the%20tremendous%20privilege%20of%20being%20around%20my%20family%20every%20day%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20early%20that%20my%20ability%20to%20generate%20income%20is%20directly%20related%20to%20my%20willingness%20to%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20a%20camera.%20Someday%20I%20may%20not%20want%20to%20%E2%80%94%20or%20people%20may%20stop%20watching.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20wake%20up%20to%20learn%20the%20whole%20business%20has%20vanished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20intentionally%20built%20multiple%20revenue%20streams%3A%20ad%20revenue%2C%20sponsored%20content%2C%20affiliate%20links%2C%20brand%20deals%2C%20and%20my%20own%20merchandise%2C%20like%20T-shirts%2C%20barbecue%20accessories%2C%20and%20my%20offset%20smokers%2C%20which%20I'm%20proud%20to%20say%20are%20made%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiversification%20protects%20me%20if%20platforms%20change.%20If%20Google%20said%20tomorrow%20they're%20not%20going%20to%20monetize%20any%20of%20my%20videos%2C%20I'll%20be%20OK%20%E2%80%94%20five%20years%20ago%20that%20would%20have%20wrecked%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2226450907-9c00-4322-b72f-f27369c45623%5C%22%3EI%20think%20about%20retirement%20more%20than%20college%20savings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20was%20a%20teacher%2C%20I%20remain%20skeptical%20of%20the%20US%20education%20system.%20I'm%20not%20even%20convinced%20I%20think%20it's%20necessary%20for%20my%20kids%20to%20go%20to%20college%2C%20unless%20it's%20for%20a%20career%20like%20medicine.%20So%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20haven't%20started%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstudent-loans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeducation%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fretirement-planning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESaving%20for%20retirement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%2C%20is%20front%20of%20mind.%20I%20recognize%20that%20I'm%20not%20an%20expert%20in%20personal%20finance%2C%20so%20I%20try%20to%20lean%20on%20people%20who%20have%20the%20expertise%20that%20I%20need.%20We%20work%20with%20a%20financial%20advisor%20who%20helps%20us%20decide%20how%20much%20to%20contribute%20to%20retirement%20accounts